node.text:
I’ve been working on different race scenes since a while now and it’s a pretty fun learning curve. One of them is this scene with the @bugatti Bolide and the… well. The king of the road. 

Who wins this race? 

It’s a long work in progress snd something I’m doing on the side of the usual design work. A little bit everyday and it’s getting there. 

Should I mention that this is fake and not real? 😂

.
.
.
.
.

I should mention that these were just for fun, and is/was in no way affiliated with any  brands or Lamborghini.

node.text:
Countach. #

No idea if this is official yet, but… 

What do you think guys, if it is, did they pull it off? 
The one thing really sticking out like a sore thumb in my opinion are those Sian style taillights. I was hoping to see something a bit more… vertically oriented this time around. What do I know? Fingers crossed. 🤞🏼😂

.
.
.
.
